message.body: Hey, lady, im in the county, what you doing this weekend?
Today not a whole lot. I think tomorrow both my parents and Adams are cooking out, so i guess I'll be eating a lot of food! What are your plans?
We're open tonight, and I'm thinking of swimming at Adams folks I'm a bit. I could be open to suggestions though!
Woo! We have to see one another! I'm going to my moms now, I will get at you when I'm coming out
Yes! Let me know. Funds are sort of limited, but err could do a drink, or even just hang somewhere. :-)
I'm broke too! Cheap handouts!
I mean hang outs!
Ha!! I like the first better!
I wish we could get handouts at our hang outs!
Whatcha doing??
We are at Adams brother and sisters place. What are you up to?
We're in town..
I fell asleep watching bill and Teds excellent adventure, like super early! I will be here tonight too, if you can hang out!
Ok! We have bbqs early, but then I'd be down to hang!
What up lady?
I just woke up. I ate bbq and fell asleep on the Willard's couch for about 2 hours... Ha.
Haha, oh trust me, I know that story, what are you doing tomorrow, I'm going to a cookout at my brothers, he lives right near your folks now
Cool! I'm visiting Linda at 3, maybe we can get coffee or breakfast before?
That sounds awesome...I loooooove breakfast. Know anyplace good?
Not...really. I haven't been out much so far. We can always just play it by ear. I'm assuming places are open tomorrow?
I hope so, I mean I feel selfish for hoping so, but..
I've worked in the service industry for awhile. You get used to it. Just as long as people don't say "thanks for working on the holiday" ha...
Oh! I hate that! Yeah, being a server for fifteen years earned me a holiday breakfast
So as a result of napping for several hours last night, i sort of... Just woke up. Eek! What time is your brothers bbq today?
Haha, that is the worst. We are at target, I don't know whats up with my brothers..
Not sure what you're up to. We stopped by square one for coffee. It's such an ugly day.
Its do gross, not good for a BBQ..we just got to my moms to get my stuff, I might be leaving soon?
Bummer!! This weekend was sort of a wash. once i start working and get money (in my head i totally sang that junior mafia style ) we will be organizing a
trip to Philly to visit you and dan ######.
Awesome, Philly is more fun anywAyz! As soon as I get to my moms I just want to lounge around in my pjs and go to bed early, ha
Yeah. There really isn't much to do here anymore. I like visiting parents who have good food and cable tv. I'm getting lame!
Haha, I know..I've been snacking like crazy
